      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms HiC-Pro has multiple external dependencies and discusses automatic installation, but does not frame this as a discrete task for manual binary path resolution. The samtools version requirement in the scope (\u22651.9) does not match the paper's stated requirement (>0.1.19).",
