      "asbval:note": "Paper lists 'Samtools (>0.1.19)' as a requirement. The card specifies '>=1.9', which is a stricter constraint than the paper's '>0.1.19'. However, passage [8] also states 'The bowtie2 and Samtools software are automatically downloaded and installed if not detected on the system' and evidence_spans in the card cite 'samtools (>=1.9) can be automatically installed if not detected', suggesting the >=1.9 constraint may come from additional documentation not in these passages. Treating as 'yes' because samtools is confirmed as a dependency with automatic installation support.",
